COMMAND:
theme

HOW TO USE:
theme list
theme set <name>

EXAMPLE:
theme list
theme set hacker
theme set neon

DESCRIPTION:
Manage Valyxo color themes.

LANGUAGE:
System

NOTES:
Available themes: neon, classic, hacker, ocean.

WARNINGS:
Theme changes apply immediately.

SEE ALSO:
man settings, man Valyxo
